- Kleyko, D., Rachkovskij, D. A., Osipov, E., & Rahimi, A. (2021). A Survey on Hyperdimensional Computing aka Vector Symbolic Architectures, Part II: Applications, Cognitive Models, and Challenges. Retrieved from https://arxiv.org/abs/2112.15424

